                                                                                                                                 2                                                                                        NATION BRIEFS
                                      
	 Ahmedabad, Feb. 1 (PTI): Seven policemen have been suspended in the city after they were found sleeping on duty, officers said today.           
	The incident took place on Saturday night when the policemen attached with the mobile police control room (PCR) were caught asleep. They were suspended to ensure efficiency and alertness among those posted with the PCR.                   
	 New Delhi (PTI): The Mysore establishment of Infosys will get CISF security after its office in Bangalore was provided with CISF guards. The paramilitary force will deploy its quick reaction team at Mysore campus, home minister P. Chidambaram said.                                                                                                                                              
